                        <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span></button>
                    <h4 class="modal-title">Selected List</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <asp:UpdatePanel ID="UpdatePanel2" runat="server" UpdateMode="Conditional">
                        <ContentTemplate>
                            <div class="form-horizontal">
                                <div class="form-body">
                                     <div class="row" >
                                        <div class="col-md-3">
                                            <div class="form-group">
                                                
                                                <div class="col-md-12">
                                                    
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-md-3">
                                            <div class="form-group">
                                               
                                                <div class="col-md-12">
                                                   
                                                    
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-md-3">
                                            <div class="form-group">
                                               
                                                <div class="col-md-12">
                                                    
                                                   </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>

                                         <div class="col-md-3">
                                            <div class="form-group">
                                               
                                                <div class="col-md-12">
                                                   
                                                   </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    
                                    <div class="row">
                                       
                                        <div class="col-md-12">
                                            <div class="form-group">
                                                <label class="col-md-4 text-primary">
                                                </label>
                                                <div class="col-md-12">
                                                
                                                     “Over the next 5-10 years, we aim to be the most valuable and respected steel company globally. The change that we need to focus on is not just one of business processes, but one of cultural change.

In order to bring this cultural change, it is important to focus on design and implement a new PMS process /which enables such behaviours at workplace. Thus, with this in mind it has been decided to design and implement a 360-degree assessment which will form a part of the new PMS process”
                                                       
                                                </div>
